{"tid":1446953,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[升級行動討論區］討論下次勇武如何升級","createTime":"2019-08-11T15:27:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T01:05:26.000Z","uid":37679,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b23c6b737ebadd961caf1f13da7acb42957328b6","tid":1446953,"uid":37679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:27:09.000Z","msg":"1. 有鬼/有狗冼低情況<br />\n一齊圍佢 用索帶綁起佢 喺額頭用Marker寫黑警<br />\n跟手搵野扑爆佢個菠蘿蓋<br />\n等佢醫返都行唔到路<br />\n<br />\n2. 增加遠攻種類<br />\n蟲、大量魔法彈、內臟廢物、雞蛋、廚餘<br />\n<br />\n3. 喺路障附近淋啲會冼既液體<br />\n倒啲點得著既油、洗潔精<br />\n冼到佢地仆街<br />\n向後撤個陣仲可以點完火先走<br />\n<br />\n以下開放討論<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黑警死全家<br />\n冇一個抵可憐</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"484b2dca0524841097236c80e656c95fd5d74f89","tid":1446953,"uid":37679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:27:29.000Z","msg":"推 一齊討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34cf1ab4e46bed10caedf7d632f7049aee5a1ef1","tid":1446953,"uid":37679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:27:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9150dae401230dd762db7b40ee91a7e6e06968f7","tid":1446953,"uid":37679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:31:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ef5d9e9f93a0164c57250c54141ac4aad25fa2c7","tid":1446953,"uid":37679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:31:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"afbec586ffeb09e1bd2a1f8deec81246160cd771","tid":1446953,"uid":37679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"